主要职责：
1. 支持制定并更新与维修质量相关的项目报告。
2. 支持制定并更新与车间管理相关的项目报告。
3. 准备技术培训材料，为经销商提供现场/在线技术指导。
4. 计划并实施针对特定主题的经销商调查。
5. 统计、分析数据并制定/更新技术现场支持月度报告。
6. 计划并准备每月的技术在线会议。
7. 计划并准备技术现场指导工作坊。
8. 完成直线经理分配的其他任务。

 任职要求：
1.	敏锐的数据洞察力，具备较强数据处理分析能力，会使用VB/Python/Tableau等编程或者可视化工具优先;
2.	熟练运用办公软件如Excel, PPT 等办公软件;
3.	具备积极主动学习意愿，责任心强，能够通过主动探查，深入了解业务内容;
4.	具备项目管理相关经验，时间观念及主观能动性强，保质保量按时交付产出;
5.	具备团队合作精神，优秀的沟通表达能力及逻辑思维能力;
6.	心态开放，有一定的抗压能力，能积极拥抱变化;
7.	熟练的英语书写和表达能力;
8. 汽车行业工作经验，懂汽车技术，处理技术case。
9.	本科或以上学历，理工科教育背景，如IT/机械/车辆/电气等优先.

Avista BV Junior Analyst Job Description: Being a member of our business valuation team, you will be led by project managers to execute valuation assignments and work for various clients including public and private companies. The valuation projects mainly includes M&amp;A transaction related valuation, financial instrument valuation, business valuation and etc. for various purposes. As a junior analyst, your day-to-day work will include but not limited to the following:
1. Build valuation model tailored for each valuation project;
2. Conduct site inspection and perform management interview with client;
3. Collect market data and perform financial analysis;
4. Perform various research tasks on listed companies, industries, capital markets and etc.;
5. Document valuation results and compose valuation reports;
6. Maintain and update industry database. 
At Avista, you will be mentored by experienced business professionals came from globally-renowned valuation firms, investment banks, consulting firms and international accounting firms. In addition, we offer systematic training and sharing events, to help you grow professionally and develop your full potential. With the quick growth of Avista, we sincerely invite young talents with the following qualifications to join us and kick off your career here: 
1. Bachelor degree or above, with major in finance, accounting or other business related disciplines;
2. Basic understanding of accounting and finance concepts is required;
3. Proficient in English writing and reading, with ability to compose emails and reports in English;
4. Excellent communication, teamwork, and interpersonal skills;
5. Quick learner and willing to learn;
6. Ability to work under pressure.
五险一金、补充医疗保险、定期体检、团建活动、5天工作制、节日福利、带薪年假、良好的职业发展前景。
